{"tid":2233835,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［左膠當道］微軟高職位增聘黑人　美國勞工部指涉種族歧視","createTime":"2020-10-07T12:15:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T09:14:00.000Z","uid":310914,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a8f5d495b976b3148631291393c58991e1a2ac2b","tid":2233835,"uid":310914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:15:16.000Z","msg":"2020-10-07<br />\n近年除了性別平等外，大眾更追求種族平等，而作為政府或大公司更應帶頭實行這種風氣。而 Microsoft 早於 6 月提出的加強多樣性計劃，希望高級職位的黑人的數字可提升一倍，卻受到美國勞工部指其有可能構成了非法種族歧視。Microsoft 最近就否認了這個指控，並直言「很明顯，這不是」。<br />\n<br />\nMicrosoft 早於 6 月時宣佈其制定了加強多樣性計劃，包括投資 1.5 億美元並使高級職位的黑人僱員人數增加一倍等。根據 Microsoft 法律顧問 Dev Stahlkopf 表示， Microsoft 上週接獲勞工部聯邦合同承諾計劃部（the Labor Department&rsquo;s Office of Federal Contract Compliance Programs）的通知，指首席執行官薩蒂亞&middot;納德拉（Satya Nadella）於 6 月 23 日宣布的倡議可能是基於種族採取就業行動，並要求 Microsoft 證明其為改善機會所做的努力並不是基於種族而決定。<br />\n<br />\nDev Stahlkopf 直言「很明顯，這並不是」，直接否認說法。她重申「我們很清楚法律禁止我們基於種族僱用員工。」，她又補充指「我們將僱用並提拔最適合的人選。我們自 6 月份宣布至今的一切都沒有改變。」<br />\n<br />\n美國勞工部發言人則回應表示，它「讚賞」Microsoft 不基於種族僱用員工的承諾，並期待與 Microsoft 合作完成調查工作。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：Reuters"},{"pid":"e708159851bd2c98d64c9aea25ca7c5510928c64","tid":2233835,"uid":310914,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:16:42.000Z","msg":"左膠公司，咁咪變相歧視其他族裔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91107b9a56d6642cf04baf179c5ece6d2f0b1aa2","tid":2233835,"uid":310914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:17:08.000Z","msg":"補link<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/10/07/microsoft-denies-americas-the-labor-department-claim-said-they-will-pick-the-suitable-choice-for-the-job-vacancies/life-tech/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F10%2F07%2Fmicrosoft-denies-americas-the-labor-department-claim-said-they-will-pick-the-suitable-choice-for-the-job-vacancies%2Flife-tech%2Famp%2F&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmTUVmWcutTvqHtF1LT7nQkc%3D&h=0127b3c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/10/07/microsoft-denies-americas-the-labor-department-claim-said-they-will-pick-the-suitable-choice-for-the-job-vacancies/life-tech/amp/</a>"},{"pid":"8db666c5bd728f56b7a37176b5c9229db07ef97f","tid":2233835,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:06:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8c8bf7823354aa2b3da8e2425aa08125c1ce9f9","tid":2233835,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:11:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"202f9b968e8a751a8b57eca8eaf64714f5c07d91","tid":2233835,"uid":263261,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:14:00.000Z","msg":"逆向歧視<br />\n究竟班高層有冇腦架"}]}